Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花開花的時候我們去賞花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有竹筍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經一年過去了呢
